{
  "text": "Bilateral LP and unilateral paretic and nonparetic KE peak muscle power were determined as the highest power achieved from 6 relative intensities of the 1RM by moving the load as fast as possible through the full ROM. [CITATION_1] ",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "34305901"
